thread.title: Kristy Mazalewski
thread.title_full: Skipper (formerly Jetaport) reviewed by Kristy Mazalewski

author: Kristy Mazalewski
title: Kristy Mazalewski
text: This is a great service. Really made it easy to set up blocks for my wedding. My booking assistant, Anne, was super helpful and very pleasant along the whole process. Successfully setup two blocks and inquired several other hotels. Thanks again!
